Hoobuwa kɛna wendu tewu hilaɣ hilaɣ nakayɩ. Hilaɣ ŋga pahʊlʊ-kɛ nɛ ndoma ɛzɩ payaaʊ ŋgandɩyɛ yɔ yaa hɩsɩ nzɩ pohosu si-taa kuhosu nɛ feziŋ weyi ɛlɩʊna nɔɔ taa yɔ ewuu nɛ pɩwɛʊ leleŋ kɛ nɩʊ taa yɔ yaa piseɣtu eyʊ yɔ.
Hilaɣ kɛnɛ kɛwɛ hɩsɩ nzi pasakɩ-sɩ kɩsaʊ nɛ kpoŋglolonaa yɔ sɩ-pɩlɩʊ taa. Hɩlaɣ kɛna kɛna kandɩ nɛ lɛɛsɩ mbʊ pʊyɔɔ yɔ, payaɣ-sɩ naalɛ kɛ ɖama yɔɔ. Ɖenɖe hoobuwa nɛ lɛɛsɩ pɛkpɛndʊ yɔ kɛlɛ se hoobuwa kʊnɛ kɩɖaʊ ɖalaɣ lʊʊʊ nɛ kɛwɛ kulukulu ɖaalakɩŋ yɔɔ ɖɔɖɔ ɛzɩ hɩsɩ lɛɛsɩ yɔ. 
Ɖooo lɔnda aseɣla takayɩsɩ sakɩyɛ taa lɛ, Egipti ɛyaa kɛ palɩza se mba kɛŋna kacalaɣ mba mba pacalɩ hoobuwa kɛ hʊlʊʊ yɔ. Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa, ɖooo lɔnda hobuwa kɛ pahʊlaɣ awiya kpaamɩŋ taa nɛ pɩlakɩ awiya nɛ abila leleŋ. Pɩwɛ ɛzɩ wiyau weyi payaɣ-ɩ se Louis XII yɔ, ɖanasɩ tɩŋga payaɣ hɩlaɣ kɛnɛ nɛ pɩkɛdʊna-ɩ.
